26
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,440
Chi Shanying ordered me
to rig the place with explosives.

27
00:03:38,270 --> 00:03:40,320
Once we receive
Shen Zhiheng's confession,

28
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,640
