- Sheng!

144
00:11:40,830 --> 00:11:41,630
Weilian!

145
00:11:43,830 --> 00:11:44,350
Weilian!

146
00:12:27,750 --> 00:12:28,920
So, you're the same as them.

147
00:12:30,560 --> 00:12:31,400
Were you

148
00:12:32,110 --> 00:12:33,750
