176
00:13:45,590 --> 00:13:46,440
Sheng!

177
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,440
You're so...

178
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:49,200
Sheng!

179
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,470
Sheng!

180
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:54,520
Sheng!

181
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:58,320
Shen Zhiheng!

182
00:13:59,280 --> 00:14:01,870
Who else is human besides me?

183
00:14:02,440 --> 00:14:04,520
Is Miss Mi still human?

184
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,160
No.

185
00:14:13,590 --> 00:14:14,630
Sheng!

186
00:14:33,990 --> 00:14:34,630
