221
00:17:02,830 --> 00:17:03,680
I'm not leaving.

222
00:17:03,750 --> 00:17:06,150
I'll hold them off.
You guys should look for the exit.

223
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:07,900
Come and fetch me once you find it.

224
00:17:08,190 --> 00:17:09,630
If not, all of us will die here.

225
00:17:09,800 --> 00:17:10,630
I'm not leaving!

226
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:13,480
Weilian.

227
00:17:15,110 --> 00:17:15,760
Mi Lan,

228
00:17:16,150 --> 00:17:17,000
listen to Heng.

229
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:17,760
Look for the exit.

230
00:17:18,430 --> 00:17:19,040
Let's go.

231
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:20,520
Come on.

232
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:43,350
Why aren't you leaving?

233
00:17:48,720 --> 00:17:49,910
