234
00:17:51,870 --> 00:17:53,000
To Mu Lihua,

235
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,560
I'm an insignificant sacrifice.

236
00:17:57,040 --> 00:17:58,830
To Mi Lan and Weilian,

237
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:01,390
I'm just a pack of walking ration.

238
00:18:02,150 --> 00:18:03,870
Instead of dying like Sheng,

239
00:18:04,670 --> 00:18:06,080
I would rather stay by your side.

240
00:18:08,240 --> 00:18:10,040
Aren't you afraid that I'll kill you?

241
00:18:11,800 --> 00:18:12,520
No.

242
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:15,240
It's because you cherish bonds.

243
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:26,040
At the end of last year,

244
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,350
during Mr. Mi's family banquet,

245
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,760
I wanted to say hi to you,

246
00:18:30,760 --> 00:18:32,000
but you ignored me.

247
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,150
You looked down upon me.

248
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:35,980
Why don't I have
any impression of it?

249
00:18:38,430 --> 00:18:40,390
Back then, I was standing beside you.

250
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:42,590
I wanted to offer you a toast.

251
00:18:43,210 --> 00:18:45,800
Mr. Shen, I'm the chairman
of the Economic Development Committee,

252
00:18:45,800 --> 00:18:46,390
Li Yingliang.

253
00:18:54,390 --> 00:18:56,110
If you looked me in the eye back then,

254
00:18:57,560 --> 00:18:59,080
maybe I wouldn't hate you this much.

255
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,760
And, all this nonsense
wouldn't have happened.

256
00:19:03,630 --> 00:19:05,480
I should've killed you back then

257
00:19:06,480 --> 00:19:08,280
had I known that all this would happen.

258
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:12,080
When?

259
00:19:12,280 --> 00:19:13,830
On the Mi family's full moon party,

260
00:19:14,150 --> 00:19:15,590
on the day when Mi Lan died,

261
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:17,110
and plenty of other occasions.

262
00:19:17,870 --> 00:19:19,560
I've spared you too many times.

263
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,590
Did you send Li Guisheng
to kill Weilian?

264
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:27,040
Yes.

265
00:19:28,800 --> 00:19:30,240
So, you hate me.

266
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:32,040
I hate you as well.

267
00:19:32,720 --> 00:19:34,040
We're even now.

268
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:37,460
♪It doesn't matter♪

269
00:19:37,740 --> 00:19:40,540
♪If I'm a human or a ghost♪

270
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:43,000
(15 years ago,)

271
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:46,670
(you frequented Longchun Opera House
in Beidu.)

272
00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:50,280
(I was just a young actor
in the opera house.)

273
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:52,450
(My sister and I
depended on each other to survive.)

274
00:19:53,670 --> 00:19:56,190
(We managed to survive
thanks to your tips.)

275
00:19:58,800 --> 00:19:59,720
(After that,)

276
00:20:01,670 --> 00:20:03,110
(my sister was dying.)

277
00:20:04,670 --> 00:20:05,870
(I begged you to save her.)

278
00:20:06,910 --> 00:20:08,390
(You left her to die.)

279
00:20:10,040 --> 00:20:12,870
(From then on,
I had no attachments in the world.)

280
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:16,870
(From then on,
I could only ascend the ranks)

281
00:20:16,870 --> 00:20:18,040
(through cold-blooded means.)

282
00:20:20,150 --> 00:20:22,590
(My hands are tainted with blood,)

283
00:20:23,910 --> 00:20:26,590
(but I still harbored
a glimmer of hope for you.)

284
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,960
(I once admired you so much,)

285
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:33,190
(yet you belittled me every time.)

286
00:20:34,630 --> 00:20:36,480
(I thought of you as
a dignified gentleman,)

287
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,080
(yet I found out that you sucked blood.)

288
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:42,000
(You tortured me and humiliated me.)

289
00:20:42,350 --> 00:20:44,040
(I hated you to the core.)

290
00:20:45,390 --> 00:20:48,480
(But in the end, I still have to admit)

291
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,150
(that you...)

292
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:51,960
(You're a good person.)

293
00:20:54,660 --> 00:20:57,380
♪It delivers savage blows to my heart♪

294
00:20:57,630 --> 00:20:59,520
It's pretty nice to die with you
side by side,

295
00:21:00,520 --> 00:21:01,480
Mr. Shen.

296
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:13,580
♪Relentlessly chasing
and thirsting for blood without remorse♪

297
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:19,980
♪Shouting alone in the bustling crowd♪

298
00:21:20,140 --> 00:21:23,340
♪The scorching sun burns me♪

299
00:21:23,340 --> 00:21:26,140
♪Leaving me restless and agitated♪

300
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:28,260
♪That long-thirsty heart beats♪

301
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:32,500
♪Once more♪

302
00:21:32,820 --> 00:21:39,220
♪The blazing flames burn me,
leaving me in a wretched state♪

303
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:45,340
♪Along this road with no place to flee♪

304
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:49,020
♪I can once again see♪

305
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:51,580
♪The blood-dripping flowers bloom♪

306
00:21:51,900 --> 00:21:54,020
♪That was also♪

307
00:21:54,020 --> 00:21:58,220
♪The passionate grandeur I longed for♪

308
00:21:58,540 --> 00:22:01,180
♪The light of desire♪

309
00:22:01,420 --> 00:22:06,460
♪The hope that surfaces before the end♪

310
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:11,700
♪The hope that surfaces
before the end...♪

311
00:22:13,430 --> 00:22:14,350
Take Shen Zhiheng away.

312
00:22:14,760 --> 00:22:15,320
Yes, ma'am.

313
00:22:20,000 --> 00:22:20,560
Come!

314
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:33,280
All the people we killed,
all the dirty deeds we did,

315
00:22:33,520 --> 00:22:34,630
were they the right choice?

316
00:22:37,860 --> 00:22:39,190
If I can't repay you in this life,

317
00:22:39,950 --> 00:22:41,000
I'll repay you in the next.

318
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:42,250
I'll wait for your return.

319
00:22:47,760 --> 00:22:49,190
Anyway, just wait for me.

320
00:22:50,910 --> 00:22:51,830
Wait for my return.

321
00:22:53,670 --> 00:22:55,280
If so, I'll trust you this time.

322
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,670
Liang,

323
00:23:03,150 --> 00:23:04,390
I'll wait for your return.

324
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:34,290
What are you doing?

325
00:23:34,600 --> 00:23:35,350
We found the exit.

326
00:23:35,670 --> 00:23:36,320
Let's save him.

327
00:23:36,520 --> 00:23:37,080
Save him?

328
00:23:37,410 --> 00:23:38,560
He told me to leave with you.

329
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,280
You'll be digging your own grave.

330
00:23:40,290 --> 00:23:41,350
Even so, I'm heading back.

331
00:23:43,810 --> 00:23:44,770
Have you lost your mind?

332
00:23:44,860 --> 00:23:45,970
Or have you fallen for him?

333
00:23:46,530 --> 00:23:47,150
Fallen for him?

334
00:23:48,320 --> 00:23:49,580
Heng intended to stall them

335
00:23:49,580 --> 00:23:51,510
himself so that I could escape with you.

336
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:52,670
If you head back now,

337
00:23:52,680 --> 00:23:54,720
his effort will go down the drain.
Don't you care?

338
00:23:55,000 --> 00:23:55,560
Follow me!

339
00:23:55,910 --> 00:23:56,670
Stop dragging me!

340
00:23:58,350 --> 00:23:59,150
I care for him.

341
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:01,960
I only care for him.

342
00:24:16,760 --> 00:24:17,480
Heng,

343
00:24:17,600 --> 00:24:18,630
she's disobedient indeed.

344
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:21,110
I would've carried you on my back.

345
00:24:32,280 --> 00:24:32,830
Miss Mu!

346
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,040
Mi Lan?

347
00:24:54,670 --> 00:24:55,520
Miss Mu, be careful!

348
00:25:10,530 --> 00:25:11,240
Superintendent Wu.

349
00:25:12,220 --> 00:25:12,830
The detonator!

350
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:14,320
Press the trigger now?

351
00:25:14,830 --> 00:25:16,150
But... But Superintendent Wu,

352
00:25:16,480 --> 00:25:18,400
Miss Mu is down below with our men.

353
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:19,860
You're still calling her Miss Mu?

354
00:25:20,100 --> 00:25:21,620
Do you think Mu Lihua is still human?

355
00:25:21,630 --> 00:25:22,760
She killed Superintendent Chi

356
00:25:22,760 --> 00:25:24,420
and plenty of our brothers!

357
00:25:24,480 --> 00:25:25,820
If we let them leave the place,

358
00:25:25,960 --> 00:25:27,800
Haidong will be in turmoil!

359
00:25:28,430 --> 00:25:29,320
Give it to me!

360
00:25:30,280 --> 00:25:30,910
Yes, sir.

361
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:39,830
As for our brothers,

362
00:25:42,190 --> 00:25:44,110
they will die for the sake of Haidong!

363
00:25:44,760 --> 00:25:46,670
They're the heroes of Haidong!

364
00:25:47,280 --> 00:25:49,560
I'll definitely make it up
to their family members.

365
00:26:48,590 --> 00:26:49,440
Sir.

366
00:26:49,630 --> 00:26:50,430
Sir.

367
00:26:50,630 --> 00:26:51,960
We're in huge trouble.

368
00:26:52,800 --> 00:26:54,000
Huge trouble?

369
00:26:54,320 --> 00:26:55,590
Did I lose them?

370
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:56,700
No.

371
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:58,300
The new superintendent

372
00:26:58,460 --> 00:26:59,920
sent his men here to talk to us.

373
00:27:00,600 --> 00:27:02,640
They want us to publish this news
on the headline.

374
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:04,540
The new superintendent?

375
00:27:04,550 --> 00:27:07,680
That Superintendent Chi, passed away due to
an accidental discharge of firearms.

376
00:27:07,830 --> 00:27:09,890
His deputy superintendent
took over his position.

377
00:27:10,080 --> 00:27:11,230
Chi Shanying is dead?

378
00:27:11,690 --> 00:27:12,640
What about Li Yingliang?

379
00:27:13,210 --> 00:27:14,230
No one mentioned his name.

380
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:16,550
Publish Wu Zhongyi's report immediately.

381
00:27:16,920 --> 00:27:18,440
The situation in Haidong has changed.

382
00:27:18,750 --> 00:27:20,390
We have to notify
the people immediately.

383
00:27:20,400 --> 00:27:21,790
- Hurry and publish it.
- Alright.

384
00:27:25,750 --> 00:27:26,920
What should we do now?

385
00:27:28,540 --> 00:27:32,420
(Chi Shanying, Leader of Haidong Army,
Died From Firearm Accident)

386
00:27:42,120 --> 00:27:42,880
How is it?

387
00:27:43,200 --> 00:27:45,230
Li Yingliang's
current situation is unknown.

388
00:27:45,510 --> 00:27:48,270
The new superintendent dissolved
the Economic Development Committee.

389
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:49,750
But even so,

390
00:27:49,990 --> 00:27:51,200
Li Yingliang didn't appear.

391
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,030
Head to the Jin Mansion.

392
00:27:58,040 --> 00:27:59,740
(Chi Shanying,
Died From Firearm Accident)

393
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:10,260
(Transport Contract)

394
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:22,460
(Haidong Maritime Industry Association
Change of Chairman Consent Form)

395
00:28:22,950 --> 00:28:23,950
Brother,

396
00:28:25,270 --> 00:28:26,470
I'm doing this

397
00:28:26,840 --> 00:28:28,710
for the sake
of the Jin family's business.

398
00:28:32,790 --> 00:28:34,790
Jingxue!

399
00:28:35,270 --> 00:28:36,510
We're in huge trouble!

400
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:37,950
Come down and take a look!

401
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:40,600
Second Uncle, I'm coming.
Stop rushing me.

402
00:28:40,600 --> 00:28:41,840
I'm here to sign the form now.

403
00:28:42,710 --> 00:28:43,600
It's not about that.

404
00:28:44,120 --> 00:28:45,990
Jingxue, hurry and take a look.

405
00:28:46,600 --> 00:28:47,470
Chi Shanying...

406
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,990
Chi Shanying is dead.

407
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:50,400
Chi Shanying is dead?

408
00:28:52,440 --> 00:28:53,360
Don't you understand?

409
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:55,790
There are new officials for a new ruler.

410
00:28:56,160 --> 00:28:59,510
Now that Chi Shanying is dead,
Li Yingliang no longer has any backers.

411
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,440
Liang?

412
00:29:02,600 --> 00:29:03,270
That's right.

413
00:29:04,160 --> 00:29:05,120
Chi Shangying is dead.

414
00:29:05,500 --> 00:29:07,030
Don't tell me Liang is in trouble too?

415
00:29:07,360 --> 00:29:08,640
Second Uncle, what should we do?

416
00:29:09,030 --> 00:29:10,230
What did I say before this?

417
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:11,990
What did I say about you?

418
00:29:11,990 --> 00:29:14,470
I said... I said you acted
on your own initiative.

419
00:29:15,000 --> 00:29:16,950
We should've published
a notice in the newspaper

420
00:29:16,950 --> 00:29:18,470
and cut our ties with Li Yingliang

421
00:29:18,470 --> 00:29:19,990
- back then!
- Pick up the phone.

422
00:29:19,990 --> 00:29:20,450
Am I right?

423
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:21,270
You argued with me.

424
00:29:21,270 --> 00:29:22,440
You argued with me!

425
00:29:22,920 --> 00:29:24,550
You threw the checkbook at me.

426
00:29:24,950 --> 00:29:26,440
You throw the piano at me.

427
00:29:27,270 --> 00:29:28,540
You went upstairs and ignored me.

428
00:29:28,990 --> 00:29:29,230
You!

429
00:29:29,230 --> 00:29:29,790
Second Uncle,

430
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:32,190
Liang didn't pick up the phone.
What should we do?

431
00:29:32,200 --> 00:29:33,950
It doesn't matter. He won't die.

432
00:29:33,950 --> 00:29:34,650
I'll look for him.

433
00:29:34,660 --> 00:29:35,990
Let's talk about it when I'm back.

434
00:29:36,840 --> 00:29:38,080
Jingxue, that won't do.

435
00:29:38,230 --> 00:29:40,640
Even if I can afford to wait,
all those goods cannot.

436
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:43,200
If you don't sign the contract now,
the dock will be stuck.

437
00:29:43,440 --> 00:29:44,920
I won't take up much of your time.

438
00:29:44,920 --> 00:29:46,390
You should
deal with business first.

439
00:29:47,200 --> 00:29:48,160
Hurry and sign the form.

440
00:29:48,310 --> 00:29:50,670
Tao, prepare the car.
We're heading to Li Yingliang's house.

441
00:29:51,180 --> 00:29:53,460
(Representative: Jin Jingxue)

442
00:29:54,600 --> 00:29:55,200
Don't panic.

443
00:29:55,360 --> 00:29:55,880
Slow down.

444
00:29:56,230 --> 00:29:57,190
You have plenty of time.

445
00:29:57,860 --> 00:29:58,660
(Representative: Jin Jingxue)

446
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,360
Here, this is the last one.

447
00:30:03,360 --> 00:30:06,120
Second Uncle, I assume there are
no opium deals involved, right?

448
00:30:06,640 --> 00:30:07,790
Who do you take me for?

449
00:30:08,710 --> 00:30:09,790
I guarantee with my life.

450
00:30:10,270 --> 00:30:10,980
Hurry and sign it.

451
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:14,500
(Jin Jingxue)

452
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,190
Second Uncle, sorry for the trouble.

453
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:20,880
Calm down.

454
00:30:20,990 --> 00:30:22,990
Slow down!

455
00:30:22,990 --> 00:30:23,640
Slow...

456
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:26,950
Slow down.

457
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,310
This is a piece of cake.

458
00:30:39,990 --> 00:30:42,990
Here it is.

459
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,310
When Jingxue

460
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:54,550
falls in love,

461
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:56,790
she becomes a total fool.

462
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:15,160
Liang.

463
00:32:23,790 --> 00:32:25,550
(Don't you know
the kind of person I am?)

464
00:32:26,080 --> 00:32:28,470
It won't end well
if you are together with me.

465
00:32:28,920 --> 00:32:30,440
(You get whatever you like.)

466
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:32,510
(Why must you be together with me?)

467
00:33:07,120 --> 00:33:08,080
(Liang,)

468
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,840
(I'll wait for your return.)

469
00:33:26,640 --> 00:33:27,310
Weilian,

470
00:33:28,120 --> 00:33:28,990
why is his wound

471
00:33:29,440 --> 00:33:30,710
