472
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:36,950
Heng,

473
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:39,080
your so-called principles

474
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,310
will kill you.

475
00:33:40,710 --> 00:33:41,550
He will never die.

476
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,990
Of course.

477
00:33:45,550 --> 00:33:47,750
