00:33:49,920 --> 00:33:50,510
Weilian,

479
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:52,310
I need to speak with you.

480
00:33:53,840 --> 00:33:54,550
Follow me.

481
00:34:04,030 --> 00:34:05,200
He's Mr. Shen.

482
