I know.

483
00:34:07,160 --> 00:34:08,520
He's Mr. Shen.

484
00:34:09,230 --> 00:34:10,200
I know.

485
00:34:10,760 --> 00:34:12,060
He's different from other people.

486
00:34:12,640 --> 00:34:14,120
If he's not Mr. Shen,

487
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,520
