488
00:34:15,760 --> 00:34:17,000
What's wrong with being like me?

489
00:34:17,310 --> 00:34:18,270
Aren't I good?

490
00:34:18,640 --> 00:34:19,390
No.

491
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:20,830
He's very good.

492
00:34:21,200 --> 00:34:22,390
He looks after me.

493
00:34:22,910 --> 00:34:24,200
He looks after you too.

494
00:34:25,830 --> 00:34:27,120
He'll cooperate with Chi Shanying

495
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:28,790
for your sake.

496
00:34:32,510 --> 00:34:33,200
That is the case.

497
00:34:33,710 --> 00:34:35,120
That's why you aren't allowed

498
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:36,350
to say something like

499
00:34:36,350 --> 00:34:37,910
