501
00:34:40,980 --> 00:34:42,040
You're his younger brother.

502
00:34:42,430 --> 00:34:43,270
You cannot say that.

503
00:34:44,600 --> 00:34:45,390
Alright.

504
00:34:46,080 --> 00:34:47,120
I got it.

505
00:34:47,830 --> 00:34:49,040
I wish to protect him.

506
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:50,750
Heng is in
a terrible condition now.

507
00:34:51,270 --> 00:34:52,390
We have to protect him.

508
00:34:53,100 --> 00:34:54,040
You have to promise me.

509
00:34:54,500 --> 00:34:56,330
Don't run away like what you did
at the mines.

510
00:34:57,310 --> 00:34:58,560
I promise you, Miss...

511
00:35:01,040 --> 00:35:02,080
Miss Mi.

512
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,660
