♪If I can no longer see your silhouette♪

521
00:36:31,804 --> 00:36:33,664
♪I would trade my lifetime♪

522
00:36:33,664 --> 00:36:37,384
♪For a moment of encounter
to freeze in time♪

523
00:36:39,124 --> 00:36:41,074
♪Break the unease for you♪

524
00:36:41,074 --> 00:36:45,704
♪Let stubbornness surrender to softness♪

525
00:36:46,454 --> 00:36:48,344
♪Accompany you in taking risks♪

526
00:36:48,344 --> 00:36:52,954
♪Hope you retain the decisiveness
you should have♪

